- Blue</code></pre><ol><li><div>Buy flour and salt</div></li><li><div>Mix together with water</div></li><li><div>Bake</div></li></ol><hr><p>This is <a href="http://example.com">an example</a> link.</p><p><a href="http://example.com">This link</a> has no title attr.</p><p><em>single asterisks</em></p><p><strong>double asterisks</strong></p><p>This paragraph has some <code>code</code> in it.</p><p><img src="https://get.svg.workers.dev" alt="Alt Text"></p><p>This is a <strong>paragraph with </strong><strong><em>nested</em></strong><strong> emphasis</strong>.</p><p>This is a <a href="http://example.com"><code>link in code</code></a></p><p>This is a <a href="http://example.com"><em>bold mark</em> in a link</a></p>"
